            "title": "Species composition and seasonal variation in abundance of Phyllostomidae bats (Chiroptera) in an Atlantic Forest remnant, southeastern Brazil",
            "creators": [
                {
                    "creatorType": "author",
                    "firstName": "Luiz Antonio Costa",
                    "lastName": "Gomes"
                },
                {
                    "creatorType": "author",
